{
  "texts": [
    "According to road traffic statistics, approximately 94% of traffic accidents are attributed to driver-related failures, including improper handling and driver distraction [1].",
    "Therefore, accurate and real-time environment sensing is crucial for self-driving vehicles in traffic scenarios.",
    "Autonomous vehicle systems use sensors like cameras and LiDAR to perceive their surroundings, detect objects in real-time, and make decisions to avoid collisions, ensuring safe driving behavior.",
    "Therefore, deep learning-based object detection methods are widely used in systems such as traffic sign detection, traffic light detection, pedestrian detection, and vehicle detection.",
    "Particularly in complex road traffic scenarios, the detection of objects like traffic signs, vehicles, and pedestrians is crucial for achieving intelligent autonomous driving."
  ]
}